    <div class="main review-item" id="2934675">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2934675/" class="title-link">理想的生活</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2934675"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/sogdiana/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1416258-1.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/sogdiana/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">sogdiana</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2010-01-15"
      class="main-meta">2010-01-15 14:52:13</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2934675_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  舒国治的文字一清如水，所到之处，形诸文字，寥寥几笔，便能得其神韵，不由得让读者羡慕起来。身在人世间，却无烟火气，像个神仙，云游四方。  读这本书，文字赏心悦目自不必多说，一字一词，一句一段，都有节奏，有用心的安排，文字之间也有呼吸吐纳，跟着这节奏进去，细细体...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2934675/#comments">(11回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">27有用 / 5没用</span>
                  </div>
