  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/8096171/" class="title-link">从《理想的下午》到理想的人生</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-8096171"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/Demon-king/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u146622984-4.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/Demon-king/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">張仕釗</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2016-09-21"
      class="main-meta">2016-09-21 23:28:04</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_8096171_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  人要任性，任性，任性。如今，已太少人任性了。不任性的人，怎么能维持健康的精神状态？他随时都在妥协，随时都在抑制自己，其不快或隐忍究竟能支撑多久？ 自己要做得了主。人生不如意之处颇多，但是想将日子过的如意的人有很多。就算你已拥有豪宅跑车，还想拥有美女钞票，逃不...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/8096171/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">45有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
